profits made on the backs of underpaid American workers goes to the top 
executives and owners. Let us make sure that America raises up ALL 
Americans, not just the greedy, shallow, narcissistic "money-bags" who, 
like Herod from the Bible, worship the almighty dollar, be damned with the
